### Import Zod 4 Core Package Using Subpath

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/library-authors.mdx

This TypeScript import statement demonstrates the correct way to import the Zod 4 Core package using the dedicated subpath `"zod/v4/core"`. Using such 'permalinks' ensures stability and forward compatibility, as they are guaranteed to remain available, unlike direct imports from `"zod"` which change behavior between major versions.

```typescript
import * as z4 from "zod/v4/core";
```

