### Configure Zod 4 Peer Dependency for Library Authors

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/v4/versioning.mdx

Library authors should update their `package.json` to include `^4.0.0` in their `peerDependencies` for Zod. This ensures their library is compatible with both Zod 3.25.x and Zod 4.0.0 without necessitating a major version bump of their own package, reflecting the backward-compatible nature of the Zod 4 release from Zod 3.25.x.

```json
{
  "peerDependencies": {
    "zod": "^3.25.0 || ^4.0.0"
  }
}
```

