### Upgrade Zod to Version 4 via npm

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/v4/versioning.mdx

This command upgrades the Zod package to version 4.0.0 using npm. After upgrading, existing imports like `"zod/v4"` and `"zod/v4-mini"` will still work, but can optionally be rewritten to the new root paths (`"zod"` and `"zod/mini"`).

```shell
npm install zod@^4.0.0
```
